@startuml live-logging-system

title Live Session Logging System

actor User
participant "Claude Code" as Claude
participant "Live Logging Coordinator" as Coordinator
participant "Hook System" as Hooks
participant "Session Logger" as Logger
database "Session Files" as Files

User -> Claude: Tool Interaction
Claude -> Hooks: captureToolInteraction()
Hooks -> Coordinator: Buffer Interaction
Coordinator -> Logger: Process & Analyze
Logger -> Files: Write Live Session
Files -> User: Real-time Documentation

note right of Logger
  • Semantic tool analysis
  • Enhanced formatting
  • Classification & routing
  • Cross-session continuity
end note

@enduml